      <h3><b>PROCESS RELATED</b></h3>
      <div style='font-family: "Public Sans", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Oxygen", "Ubuntu", "Cantarell", "Fira Sans", "Droid Sans", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif; line-height: 2rem; font-size: 1.15rem'>
        <ol>
          <li>The first step for the company is to fill in the registration form and submit it</li>
          <li>After acceptance of the registration application by CII-CESD, the questionnaire becomes active and can be accessed from the dashboard</li>
          <li>Once all the questions are attempted, the application can be submitted for review by CII-CESD. Post this, no changes to the application will be possible on the portal</li>
          <li>While the application is in review by CII-CESD, the company can view its response in read only mode</li>
          <li>After completion of review and analysis by CII-CESD, the scorecard and ESG Diagnostic Report will be available for downloaded on the Dashboard</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
