      <div style='font-family: "Public Sans", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Oxygen", "Ubuntu", "Cantarell", "Fira Sans", "Droid Sans", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif; line-height: 2rem; font-size: 1.15rem'>
        <ol>
          <li>Please attempt all questions to be able to submit the application for review. It doesn't necessarily have to be done at one go. Questions for which the response is not readily available can be attempted at a later point also</li>
